snippet.title: The Dark Delivers Gameplay Trailer [2025] [Official Trailer]
snippet.description: Welcome to your new role as Package Inspector at Postal Sector 7. Your task? Approve or deny packages after checking their contents. Simple! Dismiss any rumours of missing employees, it was probably a layoff! Above all else, finish your quota and be out by 6AM or you're fired!
